Torus combination is infinite in any direction. We can create new Torus or kill one so the
network can adapt. Vertical rings of the big Torus are connected exactly with the center of the
smaller Torus. Combination is perfect and simple!

If we translate the central torus a little up then we can see the hierarchy triangle again.

